    &none      &kp F1     &kp F2      &kp F3      &kp F4      &kp F5     &mo 5                                                       &mo 5    &kp F6    &kp F7      &kp F8      &kp F9     &kp F10       &none
    &caps_word &kp Q      &kp W       &kp E       &kp R       &kp T      &tog 3                                                      &none    &kp Y     &kp U       &kp I       &kp O      &kp P         &kp CAPS 
    &kp ESC   &hml LALT A &hml LGUI S &hml LCTRL D &hml LSHFT F &kp G    &tog 2          &kp LGUI   &none    &none   &kp LALT        &none    &kp H   &hmr RSHFT J &hmr RCTRL K &hmr RGUI L &hmr RALT SEMI &kp RET
